43rd Pique Nique Sur La Baie
Thursday, October 23rd, 2025 - 11:00am
Sarasota Van Wezel Bayfront
We are thrilled to kick off the social season by bringing back The Luncheon and Fashion Show that our community celebrated for 42 years. All proceeds from Pique Nique Sur la Baie benefit at-risk Sarasota Public School Juniors and Seniors through the Creative Empowerment Program’s scholarship fund helping students transition directly into the region’ s growing digital arts and tech workforce.
